## CopyMessageAgent API and Usage

```APIDOC
CopyMessageAgent Schema and Example:

Inputs Schema:
{
  "type": "object",
  "description": "This agent does not use any inputs. Leave empty.",
  "properties": {},
  "additionalProperties": false
}

Output Schema:
{
  "type": "object",
  "description": "An object containing the repeated messages.",
  "properties": {
    "messages": {
      "type": "array",
      "description": "An array of repeated message strings.",
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "messages"
  ],
  "additionalProperties": false
}

Sample Usage (Sample0):
Parameters:
  count: 4
  message: "hello"
Expected Result:
  {
    "messages": [
      "hello",
      "hello",
      "hello",
      "hello"
    ]
  }
```

