## Usage Example with GraphAI (typescript)

```typescript
import {
  GraphAI
} from "graphai";
import {
  anthropicAgent,
  geminiAgent,
  groqAgent,
  openAIAgent,
  openAIFetchAgent,
  openAIImageAgent,
  replicateAgent
} from "@graphai/llm_agents";

const agents = {
  anthropicAgent,
  geminiAgent,
  groqAgent,
  openAIAgent,
  openAIFetchAgent,
  openAIImageAgent,
  replicateAgent
};

const graph = new GraphAI(graph_data, agents);
const result = await graph.run();
```

